1. *Čuda* se događaju svaki dan. (Miracles happen every day.)
2. Bilo je neverovatno videti *čuda* koja su stvorili naučnici. (It was amazing to see the *miracles* created by scientists.)
3. Nisam verovao u *čuda*, sve dok nisam video ovaj neverovatan prizor. (I didn't believe in *miracles* until I saw this incredible sight.)
4. Nadam se da će se *čuda* dogoditi i da ćemo uspeti da završimo ovaj projekat na vreme. (I hope that *miracles* will happen and that we will be able to finish this project on time.)
5. *Čuda* su deo našeg svakodnevnog života, samo ih treba primetiti. (Miracles are part of our everyday life, we just need to notice them.)
6. Nikada neću zaboraviti kada sam prvi put upoznao svoju sadašnju devojku, bilo je to *čudo* koje se dogodilo u mom životu. (I will never forget when I first met my current girlfriend, it was a *miracle* that happened in my life.)
7. Mnogi ljudi se mole za *čuda* kada su u nevolji. (Many people pray for *miracles* when they are in trouble.)
8. *Čuda* su deo Božjeg plana za nas. (Miracles are part of God's plan for us.)
9. Nisam verovao da će se *čuda* dogoditi, ali desilo se upravo ono što sam želeo. (I didn't believe that *miracles* would happen, but exactly what I wanted happened.)
10. Svaki put kada se desi neko *čudo*, treba da budemo zahvalni i da cenimo taj trenutak. (Every time a *miracle* happens, we should be grateful and appreciate that moment.)